[
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4216_10164_000075_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4216/10164/4216_10164_000075_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4216",
        "content": "She glanced inquiringly at her mother.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4216_10164_000075_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4216/10164/4216_10164_000075_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4216",
        "content": "To all appearance, mrs Vanstone had been alarmed by the change in him also.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4216_10164_000076_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4216/10164/4216_10164_000076_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4216",
        "content": "\"Are you not well, mamma?\" asked Magdalen.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4216_10164_000077_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4216/10164/4216_10164_000077_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4216",
        "content": "\"Quite well, my love,\" said mrs Vanstone, shortly and sharply, without turning round.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4216_10164_000077_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4216/10164/4216_10164_000077_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4216",
        "content": "\"Leave me a little-I only want rest.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4216_10164_000079_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4216/10164/4216_10164_000079_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4216",
        "content": "\"Papa!\" she whispered anxiously, as they descended the stairs; \"you don't think mr Clare will say No?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4216_10164_000080_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4216/10164/4216_10164_000080_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4216",
        "content": "\"I can't tell beforehand,\" answered mr Vanstone.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4216_10192_000002_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4216/10192/4216_10192_000002_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4216",
        "content": "CHAPTER eleven.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4216_10192_000003_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4216/10192/4216_10192_000003_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4216",
        "content": "THE postmark and the handwriting on the address (admirably imitated from the original) warned mrs Lecount of the contents of the letter before she opened it.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4216_10192_000004_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4216/10192/4216_10192_000004_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4216",
        "content": "After waiting a moment to compose herself, she read the announcement of her brother's relapse.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4216_10192_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4216/10192/4216_10192_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4216",
        "content": "There was nothing in the handwriting, there was no expression in any part of the letter which could suggest to her mind the faintest suspicion of foul play.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4216_10192_000005_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4216/10192/4216_10192_000005_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4216",
        "content": "The minutes followed each other, and still the servant below stairs waited vainly for the parlor bell. The minutes followed each other, and still she sat, tearless and quiet, dead to the present and the future, living in the past.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4216_10192_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4216/10192/4216_10192_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4216",
        "content": "The entrance of the servant, uncalled, roused her.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4216_10192_000007_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4216/10192/4216_10192_000007_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4216",
        "content": "She decided the question of going or not going to Zurich, after a very brief consideration of it.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4216_10192_000007_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4216/10192/4216_10192_000007_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4216",
        "content": "Before she had drawn her chair to the breakfast table she had resolved to go.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4216_10192_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4216/10192/4216_10192_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4216",
        "content": "Admirably as Captain Wragge's stratagem had worked, it might have failed-unassisted by the occurrence of the morning-to achieve this result.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4216_10192_000008_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4216/10192/4216_10192_000008_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4216",
        "content": "She would have hesitated before deciding to leave England, and that hesitation might have proved fatal to the captain's scheme.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4216_10192_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4216/10192/4216_10192_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4216",
        "content": "She looked again at the doctor's letter.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4216_10192_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4216/10192/4216_10192_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4216",
        "content": "After sending to secure a place at once in the early coach, she sat down to write to her master.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4216_10192_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4216/10192/4216_10192_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4216",
        "content": "Her first thought was to tell him all that had happened at North Shingles that morning.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4216_10192_000012_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4216/10192/4216_10192_000012_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4216",
        "content": "She resolved this time to keep them strictly in her own possession.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4216_10192_000012_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4216/10192/4216_10192_000012_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4216",
        "content": "The necessary impression might be produced on Noel Vanstone's mind without venturing into details.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4216_10192_000012_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4216/10192/4216_10192_000012_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4216",
        "content": "She knew by experience the form of letter which might be trusted to produce an effect on him, and she now wrote it in these words:",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4216_10192_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4216/10192/4216_10192_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4216",
        "content": "\"DEAR mr",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4216_10192_000013_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4216/10192/4216_10192_000013_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4216",
        "content": "NOEL-Sad news has reached me from Switzerland.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4216_10192_000013_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4216/10192/4216_10192_000013_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4216",
        "content": "My beloved brother is dying and his medical attendant summons me instantly to Zurich.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4216_10192_000015_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4216/10192/4216_10192_000015_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4216",
        "content": "Pray don't be agitated! pray compose yourself!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4216_10192_000016_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4216/10192/4216_10192_000016_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4216",
        "content": "\"The impudent attempt to cheat you, which has happily opened your eyes to the true character of our neighbors at North Shingles, was not the only object which mr Bygrave had in forcing himself on your acquaintance.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4216_10192_000016_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4216/10192/4216_10192_000016_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4216",
        "content": "The infamous conspiracy with which you were threatened in London has been in full progress against you under mr Bygrave's direction, at Aldborough.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4216_10192_000016_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4216/10192/4216_10192_000016_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4216",
        "content": "I have discovered, to an absolute certainty, that the person calling herself Miss Bygrave is no other than the woman who visited us in disguise at Vauxhall Walk.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4216_10192_000017_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4216/10192/4216_10192_000017_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4216",
        "content": "My hands, I thank Heaven, are tied no longer.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4216_10192_000017_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4216/10192/4216_10192_000017_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4216",
        "content": "I possess absolute proof of the assertion that I have just made-proof that your own eyes can see-proof that would satisfy you, if you were judge in a Court of Justice.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4216_10192_000018_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4216/10192/4216_10192_000018_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4216",
        "content": "Be it so. Believe me or not, I have one last favor to ask, which your English sense of fair play will not deny me.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4216_10192_000019_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4216/10192/4216_10192_000019_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4216",
        "content": "\"This melancholy journey of mine will keep me away from England for a fortnight, or, at most, for three weeks.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4216_10192_000019_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4216/10192/4216_10192_000019_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4216",
        "content": "If, before my return, some unexpected circumstance throws you once more into the company of the Bygraves, and if your natural kindness of heart inclines you to receive the excuses which they will, in that case, certainly address to you, place one trifling restraint on yourself, for your own sake, if not for mine.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4216_10192_000019_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4216/10192/4216_10192_000019_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4216",
        "content": "Suspend your flirtation with the young lady (I beg pardon of all other young ladies for calling her so!) until my return.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4216_10192_000019_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4216/10192/4216_10192_000019_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4216",
        "content": "I make this engagement without reserves of any kind; and I promise to abide by it-if my proofs fail-on the faith of a good Catholic, and the word of an honest woman. Your faithful servant,",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4216_10192_000020_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4216/10192/4216_10192_000020_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4216",
        "content": "\"VIRGINIE LECOUNT.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
